# File header template (single source of truth)

Use this format at the top of every source file. Align with existing codebase style.

/**
 * @file <filename>
 * @module <module-name>
 * @description <short description>
 * @author BharatERP
 * @created YYYY-MM-DD
 * @last-updated YYYY-MM-DD (optional; update when making significant changes)
 * Notes (optional):
 * - Behavior and side-effects
 * - Which functions to read first
 */

Replace placeholders:
- <filename> — e.g. http-exception.filter.ts
- <module-name> — e.g. common-filters, backend-users
- <short description> — one sentence
- YYYY-MM-DD — date in ISO format
